title: Rare Hits Of The 80's Vol 72
description:
Here's part 72 of the series 'Rare Hits Of The 80's". As usual we have one more hour of obscure tunes; to take you back to experience the underground scene of the 80's. Weird underground end of music, the un-loved and unknown bands of the garage. Punk and cast off rejects of our musical culture that made all the innovations and inroads and new kinds of music but got none of the glory or the money. By the way if you're following my channel on Youtube, this installment has many of the songs you heard there recently. Tracks are are:
